  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"2.4.0-alpha01\" data-text=\"Version 2.4.0-alpha01\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 2.4.0-alpha01</h3>\n<p>March 22, 2023</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.sqlite:sqlite:2.4.0-alpha01</code>, <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.sqlite:sqlite-framework:2.4.0-alpha01</code>, and <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.sqlite:sqlite-ktx:2.4.0-alpha01</code> are released. <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/b06d4b8c52b58338b7e3a9a32bd153c0c464d224..5e7d256f82fbafb6d059ab7b18fddd87c7531553/sqlite\">Version 2.4.0-alpha01 contains these commits.</a></p>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed a <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">NullPointerException</code> that could occur in <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">SupportSQLiteQueryBuilder</code>. (<a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+/5df8698b5413f15c9e005762c988eb809f2676d9\">5df8698</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"version_231_3\" data-text=\"Version 2.3.1\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 2.3.1</h2>",
